    "text": "Department of Veterans Affairs IT Modernization Improvement Act of 2023\n\nThis bill requires the Chief Acquisition Officer of the Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) to contract with an entity to independently verify and validate the modernization efforts of certain VA programs (e.g., the Electronic Health Record Modernization Program)."
